  "response": "Preferences regarding underwear can vary widely among individuals, regardless of gender. Some guys might have specific preferences about the type of underwear they find appealing on girls, while others might not care at all. Factors such as style, color, and fabric can influence these preferences, but ultimately, personal taste plays a significant role.\n\nIn relationships, open communication about preferences can be important, but it's also essential to remember that what matters most is mutual comfort and respect. If you're curious about a specific person's preferences, the best approach is usually to ask them directly in a respectful manner.",
